<div class="ex-body">
  <p class="ex-intro">Fetal medicine is the art and science of safeguarding a baby's health before birth. Our specialists use the most advanced imaging and diagnostic technology to detect, monitor, and manage any concerns early &mdash; giving every baby the best possible start.</p>

  <div class="ex-grid">
    <div class="ex-feature">
