      <h3>3D / 4D Ultrasound</h3>
      <p>Crystal-clear imaging to see your baby's first smile, yawn, and movements.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="M22 4 12 14.01l-3-3"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Anomaly Scans</h3>
      <p>Detailed first, second, and third trimester scans to rule out congenital abnormalities.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v8M8 12h8"/></svg></div>
