  <div class="ex-details">
    <h2>Precision Care Before Birth</h2>
    <p>Our fetal medicine unit is equipped with the latest high-resolution ultrasound systems and staffed by specialists trained at leading international centres. We work closely with our obstetricians, neonatologists, and paediatric surgeons to deliver truly integrated care.</p>
    <p>Whether it's a routine scan or a complex high-risk pregnancy, our team ensures that parents understand every finding with clarity and compassion &mdash; so decisions can always be made confidently.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>NT & NB scans (11&ndash;14 weeks)</li>
      <li>Level-II anomaly scan</li>
      <li>Doppler studies</li>
      <li>Fetal echocardiography</li>
      <li>Twin & multiple pregnancy care</li>
      <li>Amniocentesis & CVS</li>
      <li>NIPT (non-invasive prenatal testing)</li>
      <li>Growth monitoring scans</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

